metadata.name: AI WORLD 1/1000
metadata.description:
AI WORLD This artwork is showing the idea of opposing or conflicting forces coexisting and being connected. The dragons represent different cultural traditions or perspectives, their Occidental and Oriental origin symbolizing the differences and similarities between Western and Eastern cultures or traditions, and the fact that they are presented on the same phone screen symbolize the interconnectedness and interdependence of these different cultural traditions or perspectives.

Duality refers to the idea that opposite or seemingly contradictory ideas or concepts can coexist and be true or valid at the same time. It's a reminder that all things are interconnected and interdependent, that the world is made up of many different but complementary aspects. Understanding this concept can help us not only to better comprehend ourselves and the world around us, but also to live in a more balanced and harmonious way
